title: Unable to reset my password
description: I tried resetting my password, but I never received the email.
resolution: The userâ€™s email was marked as spam. Instructed them to check spam folder and whitelist our email.

title: Payment not processing
description: I'm trying to complete a payment, but it keeps failing with no error message.
resolution: Identified a problem with the payment gateway. Suggested the user try another card, which worked.

title: Account locked after multiple login attempts
description: I entered the wrong password multiple times, and now I can't log in.
resolution: Manually unlocked the account and advised the user to reset their password.

title: Mobile app crashes on startup
description: Whenever I open the mobile app, it crashes immediately.
resolution: Issue was related to an outdated version. Asked user to update the app, which fixed the problem.

title: Cannot update billing address
description: I tried to change my billing address, but the system doesn't save it.
resolution: Bug in the database validation. Fixed manually and updated user profile.

title: Live chat is not working
description: The live chat feature does not load on my account page.
resolution: User had a browser extension blocking scripts. Instructed them to disable it.

title: Unable to download invoice
description: I need my latest invoice, but the download button does nothing.
resolution: Identified a front-end bug. Provided user with a direct invoice download link while we fixed the issue.

title: Two-factor authentication not working
description: I can't receive the 2FA code via SMS.
resolution: User's phone number was incorrect. Updated it in the system and resent the code.

title: Subscription auto-renewed unexpectedly
description: I was charged for a renewal that I didn't authorize.
resolution: Explained the auto-renewal policy. Issued a refund as a goodwill gesture.

title: Cannot upload profile picture
description: Every time I try to upload a picture, I get an error message.
resolution: Image file was too large. Advised user to resize it to meet upload limits.

title: Insurance claim rejected without explanation
description: My claim for a recent accident was rejected, but I didn't receive any reason.
resolution: Claim was rejected due to missing documentation. Assisted user in submitting the required files, and the claim was reprocessed.

title: Unable to access my policy details
description: I can't view my insurance policy details on the portal.
resolution: User's account was not properly linked to their policy. Fixed the account linkage issue.

title: Incorrect premium charged
description: I was charged a higher premium than what was quoted.
resolution: Identified a system error in premium calculation. Refunded the difference and corrected the premium.

title: Claim status not updating
description: My claim has been 'under review' for over two weeks with no updates.
resolution: Claim was stuck due to a backlog. Escalated to the claims team, and the status was updated within 24 hours.

title: Appointment scheduling not working
description: I can't book an appointment with my agent through the portal.
resolution: Issue was caused by a timezone mismatch. Adjusted the settings and confirmed the appointment.

title: Duplicate payment charged
description: I was charged twice for the same transaction.
resolution: Identified a duplicate transaction. Refunded the extra charge and apologized for the inconvenience.

title: Policy renewal reminder not received
description: I missed renewing my policy because I didn't get a reminder.
resolution: User's email was unsubscribed from notifications. Re-subscribed them and extended the renewal period as a courtesy.

title: Unable to file a new claim
description: The claim submission form keeps showing an error.
resolution: Form validation was failing due to a special character in the description. Assisted user in rephrasing the input.

title: Incorrect claim payout amount
description: The payout I received is less than what was approved.
resolution: Identified a clerical error in the payout calculation. Issued the remaining amount immediately.

title: Unable to cancel my policy
description: I tried to cancel my policy, but the option is grayed out.
resolution: Policy was in a grace period. Explained the process and assisted in scheduling the cancellation.

title: Fraudulent claim submitted under my name
description: I received a notification about a claim I didn't file.
resolution: Confirmed fraudulent activity. Closed the claim and enhanced account security measures.

title: Policy document download failed
description: I can't download my policy document; the link is broken.
resolution: Link was expired. Regenerated the document and sent a new link to the user.

title: Claim approval delay
description: My claim has been pending approval for over a month.
resolution: Claim required additional verification. Expedited the process and provided daily updates until resolved.

title: Incorrect personal details on policy
description: My policy has the wrong date of birth.
resolution: Updated the user's details in the system and reissued the policy document.

title: Unauthorized access to my account
description: I noticed unfamiliar activity in my account.
resolution: Reset account credentials and enabled two-factor authentication for added security.

title: Policy upgrade not reflected
description: I upgraded my policy, but the changes aren't showing in my account.
resolution: Upgrade was not processed due to a system error. Manually applied the changes and confirmed with the user.

title: Claim documents lost in transit
description: I mailed my claim documents, but they were never received.
resolution: Provided a digital submission option and expedited the claim process.

title: Unable to contact my agent
description: I've been trying to reach my agent for days with no response.
resolution: Agent was on leave. Assigned a temporary agent to assist the user.
